her </div><div class="t mf2b x1c h4 y167f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">concept of love revealed in the gospel. </div><div class="t m434 x5a h4 y1a6c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God is </div><div class="t m1367 xb3 h30 yb5e ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">agape </div><div class="t m2482 xa0 h6 yb5e ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 </div><div class="t mb61 xc6 h4 yb5e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jn 4:7, 8), and His love </div><div class="t m272 x1c h4 yb68 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and that of Christ for men is represented </div><div class="t mf38 x5a h4 yb66 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by the term </div><div class="t me31 x57 h30 yb69 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">agape </div><div class="t m1886 xaa h4 y1948 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom 5:8; Eph 2:4; </div><div class="t m1e3 x7a hb y22af ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 31 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
